Company Overview of Hussman Strategic Advisors, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Hussman Econometrics Advisors Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. It provides its services to its investment companies. The firm launches and manages equity and fixed income mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets. Hussman Econometrics Advisors was founded in 1988 and is based in Ellicott City, Maryland.


5136 Dorsey Hall DriveFirst FloorEllicott City, MD 21042United StatesFounded in 1988



Phone: 410-715-1130

