Hussman Strategic Advisors Trimmed Its Cirrus Logic (CRUS) Stake; Newlink Genetics (NLNK) Sentiment Is 1.26


					

						July 20, 2017 - By marketbeat

NewLink Genetics Corporation is a clinical-stage immuno-oncology firm focused on discovering, developing and commercializing immunotherapeutic products for the treatment of cancer. The company has market cap of $205.86 million. The Company’s portfolio includes biologic and small-molecule immunotherapy product candidates for a range of oncology indications. It currently has negative earnings. The Company’s biologic product candidates are based on its HyperAcute Cellular Immunotherapy technology, which is designed to stimulate the human immune system to attack cancer cells.
Hussman Strategic Advisors Inc decreased Cirrus Logic Inc (CRUS) stake by 66.67% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Hussman Strategic Advisors Inc sold 150,000 shares as Cirrus Logic Inc (CRUS)’s stock rose 16.93%. The Hussman Strategic Advisors Inc holds 75,000 shares with $4.24 million value, down from 225,000 last quarter. Cirrus Logic Inc now has $3.84 billion valuation. The stock increased 3.16% or $1.95 during the last trading session, reaching $63.67. About shares traded. Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS) has risen 97.50% since July 20, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 80.80% the S&P500.






Analysts await NewLink Genetics Corp (NASDAQ:NLNK) to report earnings on July, 28 before the open. They expect $-0.78 EPS, up 30.36% or $0.34 from last year’s $-1.12 per share. After $-0.72 actual EPS reported by NewLink Genetics Corp for the previous quarter, Wall Street now forecasts 8.33% negative EPS growth. 
Knoll Capital Management Lp holds 1.69% of its portfolio in NewLink Genetics Corp for 93,533 shares. Wall Street Associates owns 108,900 shares or 0.74% of their US portfolio. Moreover, Orbimed Advisors Llc has 0.26% invested in the company for 1.99 million shares. The Pennsylvania-based Tfs Capital Llc has invested 0.25% in the stock. Secor Capital Advisors Lp, a New York-based fund reported 100,529 shares.
The stock increased 0.42% or $0.03 during the last trading session, reaching $7.22. About shares traded. NewLink Genetics Corp (NLNK) has risen 49.90% since July 20, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 33.20% the S&P500.
Investors sentiment increased to 1.23 in Q4 2016. Its up 0.35, from 0.88 in 2016Q3. It is positive, as 29 investors sold CRUS shares while 94 reduced holdings. 54 funds opened positions while 97 raised stakes. 54.57 million shares or 1.99% less from 55.67 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Hood River Cap Mgmt Limited Liability Co has invested 2.29% in Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS). Nationwide Fund holds 0.04% of its portfolio in Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS) for 159,496 shares. Partner Fund Mgmt L P, a California-based fund reported 478,077 shares. G2 Invest Ptnrs Limited Liability Co accumulated 46,235 shares or 1.29% of the stock. 18,060 are held by Hillsdale Invest Mgmt Inc. Winslow Evans & Crocker owns 2,600 shares. Renaissance Group Inc Ltd has invested 0.01% in Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS). Bnp Paribas Arbitrage reported 0.01% of its portfolio in Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS). Partner Investment Mngmt Limited Partnership accumulated 10,100 shares or 0.76% of the stock. Dimensional Fund Advsr Lp holds 2.35M shares. Gareth Morgan Ltd Partnership holds 34,741 shares or 0.17% of its portfolio. Great West Life Assurance Can has invested 0.01% of its portfolio in Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS). Goldman Sachs Grp owns 570,395 shares. Wellington Mgmt Gru Llp invested 0.02% in Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS). Bb&T Secs Limited Co has invested 0% in Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS).
Since January 24, 2017, it had 0 insider purchases, and 16 sales for $9.34 million activity. SHERMAN WILLIAM D sold 166 shares worth $10,324. $300,000 worth of stock was sold by CASE THURMAN K on Tuesday, January 24. SCHUELE ALAN R also sold $150,950 worth of Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS) shares. The insider Carlson Randolph K sold $1.89M. On Monday, May 8 KING CHRISTINE sold $446,102 worth of Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS) or 7,000 shares. $1.45M worth of Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS) was sold by ANDERSON SCOTT ARNOLD. 6,510 shares were sold by Sahota Rashpal, worth $363,668.
Analysts await Cirrus Logic, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRUS) to report earnings on August, 2 after the close. They expect $0.54 earnings per share, up 63.64% or $0.21 from last year’s $0.33 per share. CRUS’s profit will be $32.57 million for 29.48 P/E if the $0.54 EPS becomes a reality. After $0.73 actual earnings per share reported by Cirrus Logic, Inc. for the previous quarter, Wall Street now forecasts -26.03% negative EPS growth. 
Hussman Strategic Advisors Inc increased Tivo Corp stake by 50,000 shares to 200,000 valued at $4.18 million in 2016Q4. It also upped Marvell Technology Group Ltd (NASDAQ:MRVL) stake by 200,000 shares and now owns 205,000 shares. Anglogold Ashanti Ltd (NYSE:AU) was raised too. 



